headline: Celsius Has Energy. This Barron’s Stock Pick Has Doubled in One Year.
summary: Celsius Holdings  was a Barron’s stock pick one year ago, when shares were trading at $32.  At the time, the energy-drink company’s stock was slumping over signs of slowing growth.  Celsius  makes healthier, sugar-free energy drinks that have quickly taken market share from major rivals like Red Bull and  Monster Beverage  thanks to its successful social media strategy that targets gym-goers and the health-conscious crowd.
